description:
Update 10/21: Added a process to pass in a TransactionId if you started the process outside of Verify. Updated the HTML nodes to handle new badged branding for each Verification 

Updated 9/3 : Added the Device Policy Check at the beginning. Update an HTML to handle the Device Policy to present a link to mobile.

PingOne Verify Flow, handles use cases for: 
Help Desk - to send a verification to a separate User
Biographical - to match users directory data to ID data
Registration - to allow the ID data to update the data on the User Object
BackUp Verification Process - Allowed for other Verified channels to be used
